# AI GENERATION STATEMENT

The concept, architectural planning, and editorial direction for this project were created by a human (xYoBro), but the vast majority of the actual codebase, styling, and algorithms were written by a Large Language Model.

Furthermore, all PDF booklets and game content generated *by* this software are explicitly AI-generated works.

